  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Chakra Control (Spirit)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 8 (Spell Level 4)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> *</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 24 | <b>Successes:</b> 7</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 12 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 28</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, E</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>If used on a mass shadow clone, it immediately becomes a normal shadow clone before applying the following. No more than two clones can be affected by this technique at the same time.<br><br>The targeted clone's HP doubles and then increases by 1 per level (up to +15). It gains a +1 bonus to attack rolls and Defense, and can now perform techniques up to Rank 6. The clone is no longer limited by range, and its duration is extended to the duration of this technique.<br><br>This technique's base cost equals one-third your current Chakra Pool, rounded up.</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Empower:</b> Spend any amount of Chakra to increase the clone's current and maximum Chakra by the same amount.</p>\n\n",
      "summary": "",
